de>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code><font face=\"Open Sans, arial, x-locale-body, sans-serif\">Element&nbsp;</font>&lt;details&gt;</code></strong>&nbsp;w języku HTML<strong> </strong>jest używany jako widżet (określany często jako spoiler), z którego użytkownik może uzyskać dodatkowych informacji.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Kategoria treści</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Flow content</a>, root sekcji, treść interaktywna, treść klikalna.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Dopuszczalna zawartość</th>\n   <td>Jeden element <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> będący bezpośrednim pierwszym dzieckiem</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Znaczniki pomijane</th>\n   <td>None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Dopuszczalni rodzice</th>\n   <td>Dowolny element&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">flow content</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Rola ARIA</th>\n   <td>Brak</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interfejs w DOM</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDetailsElement\"><code>HTMLDetailsElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atrybuty","title":"Atrybuty","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Istnieje możliwość dopisania do elementu &nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">atrybutów globalnych</a>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"open\"><a id=\"attr-open\" href=\"#attr-open\"><b><code>open</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Boolean świadczący o tym, czy element ma być otwarty bądź zamknięty po załadowaniu strony. Domyślnie jest to wartość&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;mówiąca elementowi, aby był zamknięty.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Szczypta detali<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Informacje szczegółowe na dany temat.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Jeszcze wiecej szczegółów<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Tu jest jeszcze wiecej informacji szczegółowych<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rezultat","title":"Rezultat","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Przykład sample\" id=\"frame_przykład\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details/_sample_.przyk%C5%82ad.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Jeżeli rezultat nie działa u Ciebie poprawnie, zobacz&nbsp;<a href=\"#kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami\">kompatybilność z przeglądarkami</a>, aby sprawdzić, czy Twoja przegladarka wspiera ten element.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład_z_ostylowaniem","title":"Przykład z ostylowaniem","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Zgodnie z najnowszą specyfikacją, Firefox generuje element summary jako&nbsp;<code>display: list-item</code>&nbsp;przez co może być stylowany tak jak elementy listy. Zgodnie ze starszą specyfikacją, Chrome oraz Safari posiadają &nbsp;<code>::-webkit-details-marker</code> pseudo element, który może być stylowany.</p>\n\n<p>Dla cross-browsingu, Firefox ukrywa znacznik summary poprzez&nbsp;<code>summary { display: block }</code>, a z kolei Chrome i Safari poprzez&nbsp;<code>::-webkit-details-marker {display: none;}</code>. Stylowanie może być wtedy odpowiednio przeprowadzone.<br>\n Przykład poniżej używa CSSa umozliwiajacego powrót znacznika do punktu wyjścia</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Szczypta detali<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Informacje szczegółowe na dany temat.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">summary</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token selector\">summary::-webkit-details-marker</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">summary::before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\25B6'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding-right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">details[open] &gt; summary::before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\25BC'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rezultat_2","title":"Rezultat","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Przykład z ostylowaniem sample\" id=\"frame_przykład_z_ostylowaniem\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details/_sample_.przyk%C5%82ad_z_ostylowaniem.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#the-details-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;details&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/semantics.html#the-details-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;details&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Początkowa definicja</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami","title":"Kompatybilność z przeglądarkami","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Pulpit</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>12</td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/platform/status/detailssummary?filter=f3f0000bf&amp;search=details\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">In Development</a></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/49\" title=\"Released on 2016-09-13.\">49.0</a> (49.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td>15</td>\n   <td>6</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/platform/status/detailssummary?filter=f3f0000bf&amp;search=details\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">In Development</a></td>\n   <td>49.0 (49.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td>6.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_także","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Atrybuty","id":"atrybuty"},{"text":"Przykład","id":"przykład"},{"text":"Przykład z ostylowaniem","id":"przykład_z_ostylowaniem"},{"text":"Specyfikacja","id":"specyfikacja"},{"text":"Kompatybilność z przeglądarkami","id":"kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_także"}],"summary":"Element <details> w języku HTML jest używany jako widżet (określany często jako spoiler), z którego użytkownik może uzyskać dodatkowych informacji.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<details>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<details>: The Details disclosure element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<details>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<details> : l'élément de divulgation des détails","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<details>: 詳細折りたたみ要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<details>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"details","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<details>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<details>：详细信息展现元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/html/element/details","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/html/element/details/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details","title":"<details>"}],"pageTitle":"<details> - HTML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}